Dear Heather,

Thank you for registering Elvis for Nueva York Kiddos Summer Camp!

Elvis Kabakoff  is enrolled for:
WEEK 1: July 7th -  11th
WEEK 2: July 14th - July 18th
"You will confirm dates by 4/15/25"
Regular Day 9:00 - 4:00 PM
Tuition: $645 weekly (Early bird until January 30st 2025: $595)

2 weeks Regular Day Tuition = $1290 (Early bird until January 30st 2025: $1190)
Please notice that in order to get the Early Bird Discount you need to submit the entire tuition y by January 31st (picture of Elvis Registration Form attached)
We have received $400 deposit The remaining balance is $890 or EARLY BIRD $790
If you decide to submit the remaining balance of $890 later, it will be due on June 1st, 2025.

PAYMENT METHODS
VENMO: nuevayorkkiddos@gmail.com 617-953-9324 @Yne-Leal-NYK
ZELLE: nuevayorkkiddos@gmail.com 617-953-9324
CREDIT CARD (authorization form attached, note that a 5% processing fee will apply).

A couple of days before families will receive an email with detailed information about what Elvis needs to bring (2 snacks, 1 lunch and water bottle) / what he needs to wear (swimsuit on days we go to the park, sunscreen everyday applied at home).

Please don't hesitate to contact us if you have any questions.

Muchas gracias,
Yne
